			<div class="postrow has_after_content">
				
				
				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					Re: VG Stratics Dev chat
				</h2>
				

						
						
				<div class="content">
					<div id="post_message_1364997">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							New character models = rework old ones so they don't bring quite so many GPU's to their knees. The visual difference amounts to less variety, not any &quot;new&quot; appearances.<br />
<br />
Performance <i>has</i> improved, but fro me it's moved in both directions at once. Overall smoother, but with far more pronounced hitches. I have a lower-mid range machine, so I'm used to mediocre performance, but the hitches are downright nasty. I used to get them only in town, but now I get them anywhere, in the middle of battle, etc. But my overall fps is up a good 20% or better ... when not hitching.
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="after_content">
				
                                       
                                 
				
