						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							interesting read, i give them another year before all that was discussed actually materializes.<br />
<br />
reverting bop, is a good move.  It was one of the things I hated the most.  I can understand keeping it on crafted, and reserving heroics, but bop'ing all yellows was fubar.<br />
<br />
fixing hitching, making the game playable, and getting rid of the lag should be the top priority, then adding a metric ton of high level content (whats the point of bringing new people in if they get bored at 45+?) aa's then release newbie island.<br />
<br />
I'd also want my curse of the vampire 10% stackable runspeed back! and/or make the evil eye bag (raid drop) give 10% stackable runspeed. (that was the last nail in the coffin for me)
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
				</div>
