		</div>
	</div>
</div>The Hitching in APW has been fixed. The only place in the game I still hitch is in New Targoner and my system is a year old. I recently began running the game at its highest settings and am absolutely floored by the art work and the particle effects and still dont crash. <br />
<br />
I even ran it that high while we fought Zaygius the other night and was duel boxing on the same computer. The only time I hitch at those settings is usually right before a death (ie tank dies and Zaygius turns around and pwns the raid) All I have is an HP, 3 gig ram, some sort of Quad core pentium chip, and a NVIDIA 8800GT.
						</blockquote>
